  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Welcome to the Magic Brick Realm! As a new adventurer, you need to defeat various monster enemies here through brick duel.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bug collection feedback: <a href=\"mailto:young33y@qq.com\">young33y@qq.com</a></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762650/extras/552cba0fe1eb2ea7e3a95e891e9eb6bb.avif?t=1767848050\" width=615 height=72 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762650/extras/5ca0c8228b1b75f78da874728548cda0.poster.avif?t=1767848050\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762650/extras/5ca0c8228b1b75f78da874728548cda0.webm?t=1767848050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762650/extras/5ca0c8228b1b75f78da874728548cda0.mp4?t=1767848050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong> In a single game, the enemy and you will play monster bricks on the board one after another during the round. Choose your strategy carefully and try to occupy more plots to gain more points. The side with the higher score at the end of the game will win! </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762650/extras/7f98f97923d72425269d47ed36c656ab.avif?t=1767848050\" width=615 height=72 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762650/extras/7fb078ed2a997788a2ba05d90be0032f.poster.avif?t=1767848050\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762650/extras/7fb078ed2a997788a2ba05d90be0032f.webm?t=1767848050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762650/extras/7fb078ed2a997788a2ba05d90be0032f.mp4?t=1767848050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong> Monster bricks are the main units in the battle. They have different images, sizes and skills. Sometimes they will also produce different numbers of arcane bricks as a continuation of their influence, helping you occupy more land. .</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>However, it should be noted that arcane bricks tend to be more fragile, and you need to choose to place them more carefully. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762650/extras/131b1e385202fb82f0c320aa0c3afbe1.avif?t=1767848050\" width=615 height=72 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762650/extras/5519c53b70dd10b0d6307441f2851dbb.poster.avif?t=1767848050\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762650/extras/5519c53b70dd10b0d6307441f2851dbb.webm?t=1767848050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762650/extras/5519c53b70dd10b0d6307441f2851dbb.mp4?t=1767848050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong> Various terrains may appear in a single game. Learn to take advantage of these terrains, or stay away from bad terrains. Will these terrains make your plan more effective or a mess? </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762650/extras/c595e3a26d613b55cd3ed7fd3fe2be27.avif?t=1767848050\" width=615 height=72 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762650/extras/3bba463fa95458be96f4d30e3de1c5ff.poster.avif?t=1767848050\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762650/extras/3bba463fa95458be96f4d30e3de1c5ff.webm?t=1767848050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762650/extras/3bba463fa95458be96f4d30e3de1c5ff.mp4?t=1767848050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong> You can choose new cards after defeating your opponents and solving puzzles. Choose a route to avoid risks or challenge powerful enemies. Try to build decks of different styles to improve your card collection. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762650/extras/606b710df2f73b225510956ed03de92b.poster.avif?t=1767848050\" width=120 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762650/extras/606b710df2f73b225510956ed03de92b.webm?t=1767848050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762650/extras/15e014898a154c53a608ced0b2bbe109.apng?t=1767848050\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762650/extras/15e014898a154c53a608ced0b2bbe109.poster.avif?t=1767848050\" class=\"bb_img\" width=120 height=120 /></picture></span></p>",
